You know, I’ve been pouring a lot of my energy lately into creating. writing, capturing moments, building something of my own. I started a little Patreon where I share the more personal, quiet parts of that journey, the kind of things that don’t always make it to Instagram. Maybe you’d enjoy seeing that side of me too, it's art btw. not what you think! and if it’s something you’d like to support, I’d be really grateful
